<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>500 - 服务器内部错误</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
</head>
<body class="min-h-screen bg-gray-100 flex flex-col justify-center items-center">
    <div class="text-center p-10 bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg max-w-md w-full">
        <h1 class="text-6xl font-bold text-red-600 m-0">500</h1>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-800 my-5">服务器内部错误</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-8">很抱歉，服务器遇到了意外情况，无法完成您的请求。我们已经记录了这个错误，会尽快修复。</p>

        {% if app_debug and error_message %}
        <div class="text-left bg-red-50 border border-red-200 rounded p-4 mb-4 text-sm">
            <p class="font-semibold text-red-800 mb-2">错误详情（仅开发模式可见）：</p>
            <p class="text-red-700 font-mono text-xs break-all">{{ error_message }}</p>
            {% if error_trace %}
            <details class="mt-2">
                <summary class="cursor-pointer text-red-800 font-semibold">查看堆栈跟踪</summary>
                <pre class="mt-2 text-xs overflow-x-auto">{{ error_trace }}</pre>
            </details>
            {% endif %}
        </div>
        {% endif %}

        <div class="flex gap-4 justify-center">
            <a href="/" class="inline-block px-5 py-2.5 bg-blue-500 text-white no-underline rounded hover:bg-blue-600 transition duration-300">返回首页</a>
            <button onclick="location.reload()" class="inline-block px-5 py-2.5 bg-gray-500 text-white no-underline rounded hover:bg-gray-600 transition duration-300">重新加载</button>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
